      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Dissolve <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and <strong>tomato paste </strong>in 200ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [275ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
