    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion and pepper are starting to soften, add the <strong>tomato stock</strong> to the pan with the <strong>halved tomatoes </strong>and<strong> dried oregano </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until thickened</p><p>Once thickened, stir the <strong>cooked tortiglioni</strong> through the tomato sauce and season generously with<strong> black pepper</strong></p>",
